                    <dt>Profile: One</dt>
                    <dd>key is an unique combination of: &lt;UUID&gt;/&lt;ProfileType&gt;</dd>
                    <dd>value is collection of &lt;ProfileEntry&gt; the user shall access.</dd>
                    <dd>Each User has only one of these.</dd>
                    <dt>Profile Entry: Many</dt>
                    <dd>key is unique combination of: &lt;ContentType&gt;/&lt;EntityType&gt;/&lt;EntityTypeOpts&gt;</dd>
                    <dd>value is collection of &lt;ContentTypeOpts&gt; the user shall access.</dd>
                    <dd>Each User can have many of these.</dd>
                </dl>
